## Development Commands

```bash
# Backend (Craft CMS)
ddev start / ddev stop              # Manage DDEV
ddev craft migrate/all              # Run migrations
ddev craft project-config/apply     # Apply project config
ddev craft clear-caches/all         # Clear caches

# Frontend (Nuxt)
cd frontend && npm run dev          # Dev server (:3000)
cd frontend && npm run build        # Production build
cd frontend && npm run generate     # Static generation
```

